{"tid":8598,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄羅斯第4大城葉卡捷琳堡 1.8%居民染愛滋","createTime":"2016-11-28T12:08:10.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T16:35:56.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9a16d55cd443c0c9ee134e54b488bd40531d66bf","tid":8598,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T12:08:10.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯感染愛滋病的人數急速增加，在第四大城市葉卡捷琳堡(Yekaterinburg)，有1.8%居民感染愛滋病，即每50人便有1人是愛滋病帶菌者。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯地方衛生部門副主管薩維諾娃(Tatiana Savinova)說，愛滋病在位於中部的葉卡捷琳堡快速蔓延，在150萬人口中，有27,000人是愛滋病帶菌者。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯目前約有80萬人被登記為愛滋病帶菌者，去年便新增10萬宗病例。不過，專家和政府官員表示，民眾對愛滋病認識不深，診斷性檢驗又不規律，因此實際感染人數可能多達150萬人。<br />\n<br />\n俄國官員說，新增病例多來自靜脈毒品注射，但因異性性行為感染病毒的案例不斷增加，佔總數逾四成。他們估計，若以現時速度估算，愛滋病感染人數每五年將增加一倍。<br />\n<br />\n中央社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161104/55867420\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161104%2F55867420&d=QvySEdzGX266GlvRhfVdUcW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=20db580e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161104%2F55867420&h=c5bbe365\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161104/55867420</a>"},{"pid":"7e338a6502bd653418344bf7782c33669e964981","tid":8598,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T12:11:46.000Z","msg":"叫雞唔搵俄妹了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c736d3495273fba06d2745a53ed1e5ecae0de6","tid":8598,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:35:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}